            , were indicted for <rs id="t17910914-42-off264" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910914-42-off264" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910914-42-off264" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17910914-42-cd265" type="crimeDate">23d of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910914-42-off264 t17910914-42-cd265"></join>, two cotton gowns, value 40 s. nineteen yards of printed cotton, value 30 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17910914-42-victim419" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Staves
                        <interp inst="t17910914-42-victim419" type="surname" value="Staves"></interp>
