                     <interp inst="t17910914-42-person432" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am servant to Mr. Brodie, pawnbroker, Whitechapel; on Tuesday the 23d of August, I took in a gown of the young woman at the bar. (Produced.) I am sure of the person, it was about eleven o'clock in the forenoon.</p>
